  .font-serif { font-family: 'Nanum Myeongjo', serif; }
  .font-sans { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mobile-desc { font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 1.6; }
    .mobile-title { font-size: 28px !important; }
  }
</style>

<div class="bg-white text-[#2c3e50] font-sans selection:bg-teal-600 selection:text-white min-h-screen">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 px-6 py-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center text-[#2c3e50]">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-serif font-bold text-xl">M</div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
           <span class="font-serif font-black text-lg leading-none tracking-tighter">MUA JIN</span>
           <span class="text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase">Dental Clinic</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 font-bold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2c3e50]/60">
        <a href="#about" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition">Medical Staff</a>
        <a href="#specialty" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition">Services</a>
        <a href="#process" class="hover:text-teal-600 transition">Process</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
         <button onclick="toggleDentalModal()" class="text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#2c3e50]/40 hover:text-teal-600">Login</button>
         <button class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-teal-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-teal-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-teal-100">
           Reservation
         </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 bg-slate-50 relative overflow-hidden min-h-[700px] flex items-center">
     <div class="container mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600 font-bold tracking-widest text-[10px] bg-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm border border-teal-100">
             <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-600 animate-pulse"></span> PRECISE & HONEST CARE
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold leading-tight text-[#1a252f] mobile-title">
            당신의 자연스러운 미소,<br>
            <span class="text-teal-600">진심을 담아 디자인합니다</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-md mobile-desc">
            과잉 진료 없는 정직한 원칙으로 당신의 평생 구강 건강을 책임집니다.<br>
            대학병원 출신 전문의의 숙련된 기술과 최첨단 디지털 장비의 만남.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#1a252f] text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-teal-700 transition shadow-xl text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
              Book Appointment
            </button>
            <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 font-bold rounded-xl hover:border-teal-600 hover:text-teal-600 transition text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
              Consultation
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
           <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-teal-600/5 rounded-[40px] -rotate-3"></div>
           <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1629909613654-28e377c37b09?q=80&w=800" alt="MUA 진 치과" class="rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl w-full h-[500px] object-cover relative z-10">
           
           <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl z-20 border border-gray-100 hidden md:block">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                 <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 text-xl">⭐</div>
                 <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 tracking-widest uppercase">Review Rating</p>
                    <p class="text-xl font-black text-[#1a252f]">4.9 / 5.0</p>
                 </div>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Medical Staff (Korean Doctor added) -->
  <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative">
           <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559839734-2b71f1e3c77d?q=80&w=600" alt="MUA JIN 대표원장" class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
           <div class="absolute top-10 -right-10 bg-teal-600 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hidden md:block">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase opacity-80 mb-2">Chief Director</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold">임진우 대표원장</h3>
           </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
           <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-[#1a252f]">실력과 마음이<br>머무는 진료</h2>
           <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-loose mobile-desc">
              "치과 치료는 단순히 기술의 전달이 아닙니다. 환자분이 느끼는 두려움에 공감하고, 
              평생의 미소를 되찾아드리는 과정입니다." <br><br>
              MUA 진 치과는 환자 한 분 한 분의 이야기에 귀 기울이며, 
              가장 편안하고 안전한 치료 환경을 제공하기 위해 최선을 다합니다.
           </p>
           <ul class="space-y-3 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold text-gray-600 tracking-wide text-sm">
                 <span class="text-teal-600">✓</span> 서울대학교 치의학 대학원 졸업
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold text-gray-600 tracking-wide text-sm">
                 <span class="text-teal-600">✓</span> 보건복지부 인증 치과 보철과 전문의
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-bold text-gray-600 tracking-wide text-sm">
                 <span class="text-teal-600">✓</span> 대한구강악안면임플란트학회 정회원
              </li>
           </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Login Modal -->
  <div id="dental-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] hidden items-center justify-center p-4 bg-[#1a252f]/60 backdrop-blur-sm">
    <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-sm rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl p-10 relative">
      <button onclick="toggleDentalModal()" class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-600 transition text-2xl font-light">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-black text-[#1a252f] mb-2 tracking-tighter">MUA JIN</h2>
        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-teal-600 tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Patient Portal</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Chart Number or ID" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-transparent focus:border-teal-600 rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 outline-none transition text-sm">
        <button class="w-full bg-[#1a252f] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-teal-600 transition shadow-lg text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
           Sign In
        </button>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-5 pt-2">
           <a href="#" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-[#1a252f] transition uppercase tracking-widest">New Patient</a>
           <a href="#" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-[#1a252f] transition uppercase tracking-widest">Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="py-16 px-6 bg-[#1a252f] text-center">
     <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <span class="font-serif font-black text-2xl text-white tracking-tighter">MUA JIN</span>
        <span class="w-[1px] h-6 bg-white/20"></span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-teal-500 tracking-widest uppercase">Expert Dental Clinic</span>
     </div>
     <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">© 2024 MUA JIN DENTAL CLINIC. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function toggleDentalModal() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('dental-modal');
      modal.classList.toggle('hidden');
      modal.classList.toggle('flex');
    }
  </script>

</div>
